# C4D_MMDTool Project Structure

Cinema 4D plugin for importing and managing MMD (MikuMikuDance) model/animation data. Supports PMX/PMD models and VMD/VPD animation formats.

## Directory Layout

- `refactoring/` — Plugin source code (active development)
- `res/S24_up/` — Plugin resources (descriptions, dialogs, strings, MMD data)
- `dependency/` — Third-party dependency sources (bullet3, libMMD, yaml-cpp)
  - `dependency/install/` — Compiled dependency output (generated by `init.bat`)
- `sdk_2026/` — Current target SDK project (CMake build)
  - `sdk_2026/plugins/mmdtool/project/CMakeLists.txt` — Plugin build configuration
- `source/` — Legacy source code (deprecated, do not modify)

## Source Code Structure (`refactoring/`)

- `main.cpp` — Plugin entry point (PluginStart/Stop/Message)
- `CMTSceneManager.*` — Scene manager (PMX/VMD import core logic)
- `cmt_tools_manager.*` / `cmt_tools_config_manager.*` — Tools/config managers
- `module/core/cmt_marco.h` — Common macros and type aliases
- `module/tools/object/` — C4D object plugins (model/bone/mesh/joint/rigid/morph/camera manager)
- `module/tools/tag/mmd_bone.*` — MMD bone tag
- `module/tools/loader/vmd_loader.*` — VMD animation loader
- `module/tools/mmd_material.*` — MMD material handling
- `module/ui/` — Dialogs (tools, name conversion, VMD camera import)
- `utils/` — Utility functions (all header-only `.hpp`)

## External Dependency Include Patterns

| Dependency | Include Pattern |
|------------|----------------|
| libMMD | `#include "libMMD/Model/MMD/PMXFile.h"` |
| yaml-cpp | `#include "yaml-cpp/yaml.h"` |
| C4D resources | `#include "description/OMMDBoneManager.h"` |
| C4D symbols | `#include <c4d_symbols.h>` |

## Build Process

1. Run `init.bat` to compile dependencies → output to `dependency/install/`
2. `cd sdk_2026 && cmake --preset windows_vs2022_v143`
3. `cmake --build _build_v143 --config Debug`

CMakeLists.txt automatically creates Junctions during configure via `MaxonTargets_CreateDirectoryLink`:
- `sdk_2026/plugins/mmdtool/source` → `refactoring/`
- `sdk_2026/plugins/mmdtool/res` → `res/S24_up/`

No manual symlinks needed. `projectdefinition.txt` is for reference only and is not parsed.

## Dependencies

| Library | Type | Purpose |
|---------|------|---------|
| libMMD | Static lib | MMD format parsing |
| bullet3 | Static lib | Physics engine (libMMD private dep, plugin does not include directly) |
| yaml-cpp | Static lib | YAML config parsing |
| GLM | Header-only | Math library (libMMD public dep) |

Debug libraries use `_Debug` suffix (e.g. `libMMD_Debug.lib`).
